      "text": "The research approach adopted in this project is the action research method. To this end, it identifies stakeholders in the conflict between Pastoralists and Farmers in Saki-West Local Government Area and interviewed over 60 subjects using the focus group discussion technique. Such stakeholders include Farmers, Fulani Herdsmen, Hunters, MIYETTI/ALLAH, Traditional Rulers in Saki, Security Agencies as well as State-and Local Government functionaries were also interviewed.  Furthermore, secondary data was collected from the internet and other reliable sources on similar conflict situations in and outside Nigeria. "
